Install Project From GitHub 

if (!require("devtools")) {
    install.packages("devtools")    
}
devtools::install_github("fpahlke/demoProject1")

Load Project 

library(demoProject1)

Load Data 

data <- load_data(system.file("extdata", "data.csv", package = "demoProject1"))

Summarise Data 

data_clean <- filter_complete(data, "age")
summarise_parameter(data_clean, "age")
#> $param_name
#> [1] "age"
#> 
#> $mean
#> [1] 50.12918
#> 
#> $sd
#> [1] 19.25734
summarise_parameter(data_clean, "bmi")
